Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:30.82,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}The promise we never made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:31.57,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:36.45,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}tries to snatch our future away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:41.83,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}Why is it that we can't rejoice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.04,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}straight from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:48.01,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}when we obtain something we've always been after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:53.68,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,358}The overflowing tears aren't from feebleness or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:58.43,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,0)}They're fragments born from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:03.56,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Of all the moments and destinies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:12.24,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I realized there's one absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.87,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Even if things get tough and I'm at my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:18.87,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I refuse to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:23.63,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Please, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:31.76,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can feel the warmth of your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:35.26,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}where it's tightly joined with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:30.82,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kawashita hazu no nai yakasoku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:31.57,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kyou mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:36.45,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Bokura no mirai wo ubaou to suru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:41.83,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}Hoshigatteita mono wo te ni shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.04,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Sunao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:48.01,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Umaku waraenai nowa nazedarou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:53.68,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,358}Afureru namida wo yowasa ya koukai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:58.43,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,0)}Itami ga unda kakera de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:03.56,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Donna shunkan datte unmei datte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:12.24,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Hitotsu dake tashika na mono ga aru to shitta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.87,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Genkai datte konnan datte
