Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:39.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.24,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I think you owe me an explanation, Wrath...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,My past memories won't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,They're making so much noise inside my head!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.71,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why is King Bradley inside of my memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.76,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.22,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to my belongings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.73,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,This is your greed, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:13.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool who craves even his past,\Nwithout knowing how to let anything go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:16.82,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, Sir Selim, are you two all right as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.87,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The guards didn't even stand a chance against him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.42,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,No, worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He was quite powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.02,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.98,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,hurry up and retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.86,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Olivier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.65,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You come home after such a long time,\Nand that's the first thing you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:48.49,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to spend the remainder of your life in peace after naming me the head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.37,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to have Alex succeed the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.75,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,A coward like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:04:00.38,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Why not transfer all of the family property and go on a long vacation to a foreign country or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:05.59,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Alex would be nothing but a hindrance to the Armstrong name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.64,Default,Alex,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.85,Default,Alex,0000,0000,0000,,So you were home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.19,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:16.90,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.90,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Duel with Olivier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.19,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.69,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The victor shall inherit the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.57,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,How does that sound, Olivier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.62,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.91,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,A plausible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:33.46,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Olivier told me to retire and to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.71,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.54,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What an insult to our father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.96,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:52.06,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you what my muscles are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.69,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Quite brave of you, Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.06,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon see how inexperienced you truly are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.61,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.99,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.08,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,So, where should we go for vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.79,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,How about Xing, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.71,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the food is wonderful there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.58,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Xing it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.25,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.04,Default,Cath,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.26,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.02,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.89,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on killing me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.31,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It took you {\i1}this{\i0\fscx40} {\r} long to notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.52,Default,Cath,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.57,Default,Cath,0000,0000,0000,,What should we get for them as souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.45,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What about an elephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.32,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,They're big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.49,Default,Cath,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd like one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.88,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.51,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear the outcome has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:20.40,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to inherit everything\Nowned by the Armstrong family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.81,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:26.82,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've been quite familiar with the upper echelon lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.32,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.70,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not know what they're-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.45,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to see things with my own eyes before making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.62,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,So after you saw their true intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you had the family flee the country in order to keep them safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.84,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,The defeated should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.80,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the easternmost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you keep going, you'll only find a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.96,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I was planning on going back to my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your country?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.54,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to cross the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.17,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.47,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl like you is going to cross the desert by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.47,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get something together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out some food and the like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.35,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.81,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so restrained!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.06,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why not stay here for the night\Nand leave for your trip tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.07,Default,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,You can use our bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.65,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Steve, you've got an extra room at your place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let her stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.57,Default,Steve,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.08,Default,Steve,0000,0000,0000,,My eldest daughter's room is open right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Emmy, who left for the university in Central, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's too perfect to be your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.75,Default,Steve,0000,0000,0000,,Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.00,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,We also need to feed this little kitty something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.55,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! You must be really hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.92,Default,Steve,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's not just looking at {\i1}you{\i0\fscx40} {\r} as its next meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.34,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.01,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, right, Kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.93,Default,Steve,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's saying that you look tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.85,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice people, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.44,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:38.87,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you'll gain anything from\Nbringing back a half-dead homunculus like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:46.17,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you go to Central, you'll be able to learn the true method to gain immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.25,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to save these people as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:56.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't mean much to you,\Nsince you're on your way back to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.44,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for your kindness, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.36,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.23,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I still have something I need to take care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.15,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Central!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.03,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a moron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.20,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you go back to Central, the cards will be in my favor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I obtain a philosopher's stone, I can return to my original form.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I obtain one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.69,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hideout we've used before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.03,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where your little brother is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred percent positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al will definitely be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.32,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.95,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.16,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.08,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an unreliable brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.75,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,So we came all the way down here for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No... is it Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.73,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You always eat so much, doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.50,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,So much for our emergency provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.51,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those two? Your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Meet Donkey Kong and Li-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.26,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Darius!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.59,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Heinkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:06.26,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be in the army, but we're working with this brat right now for various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.22,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well... how should I explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.48,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.52,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Homun-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Why can't you keep your mouth shut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.48,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, what the hell are you doing here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.79,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed cut all ties with the other homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I took advantage of his restlessness at that point to get my body back from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.92,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for a place near Central where I could rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.13,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,and I found this shed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.63,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.51,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed's trying to take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out! Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.56,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:59.90,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That 'Father' guy who lurks beneath Central is going to open the gate on "The Day".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.45,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I can only speculate since I'm an amateur at this sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:08.16,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,but wouldn't you and Al be able to get your bodies back if you two leap into that gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but you need to pay a toll to open the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is he opening the gate for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said "The Day", does he already know when he's going to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.44,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take over just yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.31,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The message...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:41.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you deliver my message... to Lan Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Message"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al delivered it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where she is now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm glad to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.05,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't hold out any... longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.56,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.31,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Blabbering on and on...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.39,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.02,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.90,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:25.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to let us go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.49,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.24,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to what this guy was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.54,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I cut ties with the homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:40.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it and attacked Bradley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.34,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know {\i1}what{\i0\fscx40} {\r} they'll do to me if I go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:47.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm just going to run off\Nlike this and live an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.38,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got nowhere else to go, then come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.36,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Join you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.36,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Join you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.87,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.74,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.50,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,This entire world belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:20.54,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,If {\i1}you{\i0\fscx30} {\r} want to work under {\i1}me{\i0\fscx30} {\r}, I just might consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.29,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.81,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:40.10,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got so many souls inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.19,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I'm... alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.86,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you join up with Ed and them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.78,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like that, then give me back my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.37,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Emperor of Xing and fill up the emptiness in your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,An emperor of a country, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.33,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Big dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.87,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.13,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to go that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you strive to become the King of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.64,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,King of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.02,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What? You guys are so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.98,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even care which one you are anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just to make it easier, I'll call you Gredlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.73,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you calling Gredl-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work under you, Gredlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:28.82,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'll work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:37.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Which means these two chimeras working with me will be working for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.41,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.62,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.08,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.25,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so cocky, you runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.17,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Midget! Flea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:55.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the moment I decided to become a dog of the military, I threw away all my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I don't really care if I have to wag my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:04.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,it would be dumb to lose this opportunity to get information by having my pride take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The chance of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.36,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.41,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let your strong feelings take over like that and lose important information?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.62,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.37,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming one of my men also means becoming an outcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.75,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You better not regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've done far worse than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.00,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.76,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.88,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Then you two are my men as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.09,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.76,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who I follow as long as I get to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.02,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Just out of curiosity, what kind of chimeras are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.10,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.64,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Lion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.35,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I still have her earrings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:53.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I won't be seeing Winry and Al for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"The Day"... huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.33,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, stop coming here all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.25,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,I even said I'd let you know when Miss Izumi returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.96,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep visiting like this, we'll go out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.39,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,Curtis butcher shop, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.51,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're always glad to have your business, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.89,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,The one you ordered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.98,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,Come back as a customer for once, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:30.73,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, the soldiers were here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.11,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.61,Default,Mason,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for you from Alphonse and a man named Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.07,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.75,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a pretty big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.08,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.08,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.34,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,The promised day, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and contact headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.77,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,This is Point Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.97,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Drachman forces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.60,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How many men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:09.85,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,One?! Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm asking who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Point Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A housewife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.45,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}Frontier troops randomly assaulted by a mysterious woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.96,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like what happened around twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.21,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,They were all beat down by one force?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.88,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,They're really going to get killed by the Major General when she returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Major Miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.51,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,An Ishbalan with dark glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.39,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and a large man with a mohawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.81,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you two to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.65,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.15,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm a passing housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for you from Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Can we speak in private?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.79,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a message from Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.54,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,All that was contained in the message is "The Promised Day".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.21,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.92,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Very fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.88,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Things are really starting to get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.22,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.60,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills are as good as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.52,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.52,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Your butt is as sexy as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.69,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Lieutenant General Grumman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.11,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't let your guard down on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.11,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're friends with Lieutenant Hawkeye, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.91,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Riza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.29,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:56.67,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,They rescheduled the joint training between the north and the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.80,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,You know, because of that battle between Drachma and Briggs from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.43,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's planned to take place in the east, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.72,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:11.43,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,First, Colonel Mustang, now, the Führer President...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:15.56,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me to some hot guys in Central, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.48,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Here's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.61,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.15,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Your master is heartless! She's stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.07,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:30.29,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to marry some rich guy and retire already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.04,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.04,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Second Lieutenant Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.29,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.63,Default,Rebec,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.22,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,"Give my regards to Second Lieutenant Havoc", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:58.40,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about transferring to a hospital in the east once my body settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.98,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get lonely around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known that, I would have brought you something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.20,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.78,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,One cigarette a day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.33,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.83,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I just ran out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.75,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll visit you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.96,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.83,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.46,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.83,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Okie dokie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.17,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,If the Colonel visits, please give him my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.55,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.05,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.93,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to hide like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're both being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be bad if they get suspicious of us after meeting in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.94,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.74,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,How about a smoke, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.83,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just one for the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.13,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,"In the following Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.18,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,on the promised day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.85,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,both the north and the east will make their move."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:02.71,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the Spring of next year, the people harden their resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:07.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The boy heads for the enemy's lair with determination in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:13.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:16.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 46, Looming Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:21.98,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're far apart, their hearts are linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:25.35,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're both on the move.
